CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 5, 1960, pg. A2, reads: "Top Union Official - Charles Larry (center), shown with Frank Blythe, left, and Ellis Hockenberry, president and secretary, respectively, of IUE Local 746, Columbus, Ohio, recently was chosen executive vice president of the 40,000 member Columbus-Franklin County AFL-CIO. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Charles Larry wearing moustache, striped tweed suit jacket, and patterned bow tie, posed seated on corner of desk
